  "detailed_description": "<h1>Comparative Grid</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345820/extras/2044e98e4e5568b8905466292973023c.avif?t=1761311405\" width=800 height=785 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your hammers and pound the drums to epic tracks, from celtic rock to viking power metal. With dozens of official songs and thousands of community-made tracks, enjoy hours of fun as you play in perfect sync to carve your name on top of the leaderboard and race against your rivals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚡<strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>46 songs</strong> in the base game from bands like Alestorm, Gloryhammer, Electric Callboy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 DLC adding <strong>49 extra tracks</strong> from bands like Sabaton, Miracle of Sound, Nightwish, The Offspring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to play, hard to master with <strong>3 difficulty levels</strong> for each song</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4500+ community-made tracks via<strong> custom song</strong> support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Public or private <strong>online PvP</strong> multiplayer (up to 6 players)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local split-screen</strong> mode for couch competition (up to 4 players)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solo races</strong> against your own best records as ghost ships</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VR compatible</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cross-platform multiplayer </strong>(PC & VR players together)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lots of stylised Nordic environments</strong> inspired by Viking mythology</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎶<strong>DLC LIST:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345820/extras/534321adb9a1fab5f5a3e8db24e3cacf.avif?t=1761311405\" width=800 height=1263 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your hammers and pound the drums to epic tracks, from celtic rock to viking power metal. With dozens of official songs and thousands of community-made tracks, enjoy hours of fun as you play in perfect sync to carve your name on top of the leaderboard and race against your rivals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚡<strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>46 songs</strong> in the base game from bands like Alestorm, Gloryhammer, Electric Callboy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 DLC adding <strong>49 extra tracks</strong> from bands like Sabaton, Miracle of Sound, Nightwish, The Offspring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to play, hard to master with <strong>3 difficulty levels</strong> for each song</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4500+ community-made tracks via<strong> custom song</strong> support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Public or private <strong>online PvP</strong> multiplayer (up to 6 players)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local split-screen</strong> mode for couch competition (up to 4 players)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solo races</strong> against your own best records as ghost ships</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VR compatible</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cross-platform multiplayer </strong>(PC & VR players together)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lots of stylised Nordic environments</strong> inspired by Viking mythology</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎶<strong>DLC LIST:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345820/extras/534321adb9a1fab5f5a3e8db24e3cacf.avif?t=1761311405\" width=800 height=1263 /></span></p>",
